#N canvas 40 40 780 620 12;
#X text 20 16 melodytest.pd -- headless check of the pitch generator + note-send gate. mode-table loads the scale. A metro toggles a 1/0 touch/release gate into note-send (intensity fixed at 0.7) \; on touch melodic-voice advances and note-send prints a note-on [pitch velocity] pair \, on release it prints a note-off [lastpitch 0] pair. Quits after ~3 s. Run: pd -nogui -noaudio -stderr -path pd pd/test/melodytest.pd;
#X obj 40 110 mode-table;
#X obj 40 470 note-send;
#X obj 260 410 melodic-voice 0;
#X obj 40 540 print MELODY;
#X obj 360 70 loadbang;
#X obj 360 110 t b b b;
#X msg 360 250 octave 0;
#X msg 520 160 0.7;
#X obj 40 410 metro 400;
#X obj 360 160 del 300;
#X msg 360 200 1;
#X obj 40 300 f 1;
#X obj 150 300 + 1;
#X obj 150 340 mod 2;
#X obj 600 110 del 3200;
#X msg 600 160 0;
#X msg 600 210 \; pd quit;
#X connect 5 0 6 0;
#X connect 5 0 15 0;
#X connect 6 2 7 0;
#X connect 6 1 8 0;
#X connect 6 0 10 0;
